sellerCard.oneLiner: Multiskilled Pro with 8 Years of Experience
sellerCard.description:
Hi, I’m Muhammad Abbas – A Multiskilled Pro with 8+ Years of Experience!

I’m a PHP Developer, Web Designer, and Certified Google Ads Expert. I specialize in building custom PHP applications, creating responsive websites, and running high-converting ad campaigns.

Additionally, I’m an ACCA Finalist, Certified in Excel & Power BI, and experienced in Pakistani/UK Tax, Accounting Audits, and Banking.

Whether you need web development, digital marketing, or financial expertise, I’m here to help! Let’s work together to achieve your goals.

Regards,
Muhammad Abbas

I am offering development and designing of E Wallet Website using PHP Framework.

Key Features :

Multi Language Supported.

Email Notifications.

High Security Includes (2 Factor Auth & Google Auth)

Multiple Automatic Deposit Methods Includes ( Stripe, PayPal, Skrill, AdvCash, Perfect Money, Payeer, Bank Transfer)

All Transaction History

Thanks

questionsAndAnswers.question: Website or App?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will develop you a e-wallet website, with mobile responsive web pages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Multiple Gateways?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, We added multiple gateways in the script. 
However you can add more gateway for manual processing too.
